article_title: Tenet Hospitals See Uninsured Fall In States That Expanded Medicaid

article_metadata.description: Tenet Healthcare is seeing an increase in uninsured patients and bad debt at its hospitals, though facilities in states that expanded Medicaid coverage for poor Americans under the Affordable Care Act reap more paying customers and lower uncompensated care expense.
